Features:
* Accept file
* Get user's choice
* Count word
* Count characters
* Count lines

Classes:
* Java.Counter (Functional Interface)
* Java.Manager
* Java.LineCounter (implements Java.Counter)
* Java.WordCounter (implements Java.Counter)
* Java.CharacterCounter (implements Java.Counter)

Functional Interface:
Java.Counter
Fields:
int count;

abstract method:
getCount(File file);

Static method:
public static boolean verifySpecialCharacter(String word)


Java.Manager:
Fields:
private int choice
private File file
private Scanner reader

Methods:
public void printChoice()
public int getChoice()
main()
public File validateFile(File file)


Java.CharacterCounter:
public int getCount(File f) (Overridden)

Java.WordCounter:
public int getCount(File f) (Overridden)

Java.LineCounter:
public int getCount(File f) (Overridden)
